      <title>华盛顿寻求答案，美墨边境移民激增导致贸易放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/migrant-surge-us-mexico-border-slows-trade-washington-seeks-answers-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于最近几天移民过境人数增加，当局关闭了两个过境点，铁路公司和商业团体正在敦促美国政府重新开放德克萨斯州和墨西哥边境的贸易路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/migrant-surge-us-mexico-border-slows-trade-washington-seeks-answers-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 11:06:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊拉克什叶派执政联盟赢得100多个地方议会席位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraqs-shiite-ruling-alliance-wins-more-than-100-local-council-seats-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据伊拉克官方媒体报道，伊拉克什叶派执政联盟的各党派在本周举行的省议会选举中总共获得了 285 个席位中的至少 101 个席位，成为单一最大席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraqs-shiite-ruling-alliance-wins-more-than-100-local-council-seats-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 11:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
