      <title>教皇支持检察官针对的意大利移民救援组织</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/pope-backs-italian-migrant-rescue-group-targeted-by-prosecutors-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[教皇弗朗西斯周三公开支持意大利移民海上救援慈善机构，该慈善机构的成员面临教唆非法移民的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/pope-backs-italian-migrant-rescue-group-targeted-by-prosecutors-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 11:01:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
