      <title>巴西“鹅特工”在越狱时鸣叫</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazilian-geese-agents-honk-case-prison-break-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴西南部圣卡塔琳娜州的一所监狱周围，鹅们摇摇晃晃地走来走去，在巡逻中击败了它们的犬类前辈，以确保囚犯不会逃跑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazilian-geese-agents-honk-case-prison-break-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 10:06:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
