      <title>以色列制定了治疗被释放的儿童人质创伤的未知方法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-charts-unmapped-ways-treat-trauma-freed-child-hostages-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在哈马斯在 10 月 7 日的暴乱中绑架了超过 35 名儿童和青少年几天后，以色列的青少年心理学家和福利专家开始忧心忡忡地为他们的回归做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-charts-unmapped-ways-treat-trauma-freed-child-hostages-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 09:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
