      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-battles-hamas-streets-gaza-city-un-delays-vote-again-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚通常只有在看起来有可能取得进展时才公开干预外交。消息人士称，特使们正在讨论根据新的停战协议，哪些仍被扣押在加沙的人质可以被释放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-battles-hamas-streets-gaza-city-un-delays-vote-again-2023-12-20/</guid>
